Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Étoile de Poudre !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:47.78,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Mince !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.06,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Étoile de Poudre !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.26,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Étoile de Poudre !
